      <br>
      <h3 class="">Step One</h3>
      <p>
        To obtain the token, corporate id, and api key, check
        <a
          href="https://experienceleague.adobe.com/docs/analytics-learn/tutorials/apis/using-postman-to-make-adobe-analytics-2-0-api-requests.html?lang=en"
